    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable daily driver for an owner who values functionality over aesthetics. The exterior shows some age with noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor dings along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows signs of regular use and minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may eventually require routine maintenance for older components. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic project opportunity! This vehicle is definitely a 'diamond in the rough' and will need significant mechanical work and some serious TLC to get it back in tip-top shape. It\u2019s the perfect choice for a mechanic or a hobbyist looking for a budget-friendly challenge with plenty of potential once restored!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
